	see Joh 10:7-9.  https://www.blueletterbible.org/kjv/jhn/10/7-9/s_1007007
	<a href="https://www.blueletterbible.org/kjv/jhn/10/7-9/s_1007007" target="_blank">
		John 10:7-9
	</a>
	and see
	<a href="https://www.blueletterbible.org/kjv/deu/6/9/s_159009" target="_blank">
